@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qekutw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.39
    v1 = v2
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.41) - 0.14)
    v1 = v0
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.76) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.49)) + v1)
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.77 * v2 + 0.26)) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.23) / 0.20))
    data[tid] = v0
